00:00:00,213 --> 00:00:02,187
Smithy: Who goes there!? Oh, it's a young girl.

2
00:00:02,212 --> 00:00:03,640
Don't touch anything!

3
00:00:03,665 --> 00:00:06,473
People steal me blind; I know you all hate me!

4
